{
    "inner": "Her compliment made me feel a little more comfortable. I'm glad I put in the effort to dress up tonight.",
    "speak": "Thank you so much, that's really sweet of you to say.",
    "action": null
}

{
    "inner": "I appreciate that she's trying to make conversation, but I don't want to bore her with details.",
    "speak": "My day was good, just busy with work and errands. What about yours?",
    "action": null
}

{
    "inner": "It sounds like we both had a pretty average day. I'm still trying to figure out if there's a real connection between us.",
    "speak": "I know the feeling. Sometimes you just need to unwind after a long day. Is there anything in particular that you like to do to relax?",
    "action": "Take a small bite of bread and butter while attentively listening to her response."
}

{
    "inner": "I'm glad we have some common interests, maybe we can go to a bookstore or concert together sometime. I should tell her what I like to do in my free time.",
    "speak": "I like to go for runs and hang out with friends. But recently, I've been spending a lot of time watching crime documentaries on Netflix.",
    "action": null
}
